  <title id="GUID-EA82D1DF-CCBC-4C3B-AB89-ECC1707C992B">ModifyVolume</title>
  <shortdesc>You can use the <apiname>ModifyVolume</apiname> method to modify settings on an existing volume. You can make modifications to one volume at a time and changes take place immediately. </shortdesc>
